name: Automatic Speech Recognition System
description: Developed an ASR using Hugging Face wav2vec model. Generated a Speech corpus for the Urdu language containing all distinctive phonemes. Code is private due to academic code regulations

name: Video Object Detection System
description: Video Object Detection using Yolov5 and Seq NMS. This project improves existing Object Detection Framework (Yolov5) using non-sequential maximal suppression algorithm
